ass="_ _8"></span>人在死亡时，<span class="_ _6"></span>会流下三滴泪，<span class="_ _8"></span>所</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya3 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">以也是哭着死去。<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls21">我们在生活中会有很多痛苦，<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls26">所谓的幸福，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya4 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">实际上也是痛苦。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 ye9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学习这些道理以后，<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls16">一定要去修持。<span class="_ _b"></span>仅仅是理论上了知，</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y99 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">在痛苦降临时，<span class="_ _8"></span>仍然会无法承受。<span class="_ _8"></span>我平时也讲过：<span class="_ _8"></span>开车的时</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
